imdb.plot outline: After Ana Leal and her best friend, Jennifer, lose their home in a tragic fire she finds herself in harsh debt and in need of a second job. Destiny brings her to the mischievous Lascurain kids who have faced their own tragedy. Ana is faced with a series of events that would change her life and the Lascurain kids forever.
imdb.title: My Heart Is Yours
plot: A poor woman loses her house and gets a job as a nanny taking care of 7 kids.::spmelendezps

After Ana Leal and her best friend, Jennifer, lose their home in a tragic fire she finds herself in harsh debt and in need of a second job. Destiny brings her to the mischievous Lascurain kids who have faced their own tragedy. Ana is faced with a series of events that would change her life and the Lascurain kids forever.
